Model analysis. To assess model quality, we used built-in measures such as omission rate and area under the 
ROC
curve (AUC). For the analysis of variable contributions, we used data on percent contribution, permutation importance, and performed the jackknife test. We considered that characteristics such as percent contribution should be interpreted with caution (

